hadiths[184]{hadithnumber,text}:
5043,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aagah raho ! jo shakhs shib-hey-Amad wali surat mein ghalati sey maara jaey, maslan : kodey aur dandey waghera sey, uski diyat sau oont hai jin mein sey chaalis oontniyaan hamila hongi."
5044,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aagah raho ! jo shakhs shib-hey-Amad wali surat mein ghalati sey maara jaey, maslan : kodey aur dandey waghera sey, uski diyat sau oont hai jin mein sey chaalis oontniyaan hamila hongi."
5045,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka key din khutba irshad farmaya. (us mein) aap ney farmaya : aagah raho ! jaan boojh kar kiye gaye shubhey ki surat mein kodey, dandey ya patthar key sath ghalati sey maarey janey waley shakhs ki diyat sau oont hai jin mein sey chaalis saniya (paanch saal ki oontni) sey bazil (aath saal ki oontni) aam tak hon aur un mein sey har eik hamila ho."
5046,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney fateh Makka key din khutba irshad farmaya. (us mein) aap ney farmaya : aagah raho ! jaan boojh kar kiye gaye shubhey ki surat mein kodey, dandey ya patthar key sath ghalati sey maarey janey waley shakhs ki diyat sau oont hai jin mein sey chaalis saniya (paanch saal ki oontni) sey bazil (aath saal ki oontni) aam tak hon aur un mein sey har eik hamila ho."
5047,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aus sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kodey ya dandey, sontey key sath ghalati sey maara jaey, uski diyat mughalliza (gandi), yani sakht hogi, sau oont jin mein sey chaalis oontniyaan hamila hon."
5048,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aus sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kodey ya dandey, sontey key sath ghalati sey maara jaey, uski diyat mughalliza (gandi), yani sakht hogi, sau oont jin mein sey chaalis oontniyaan hamila hon."
5049,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey manqul hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key din Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap ney farmaya : aagah raho ! jo shakhs ghalati sey shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein maara jaey kodey aur dandey,sontey key sath to uski diyat key oonton mein chaalis oontniyan aisi hun jinkey pet mein bachchey hon."
5050,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey manqul hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key din Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to aap ney farmaya : aagah raho ! jo shakhs ghalati sey shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein maara jaey kodey aur dandey,sontey key sath to uski diyat key oonton mein chaalis oontniyan aisi hun jinkey pet mein bachchey hon."
5051,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi ney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab fateh Makka key moqe par Makka Mukarrama tashrif laye to aap ney farmaya : aagah raho ! jo maqtool shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein ghalati sey kodey ya dandey, sauntey sey maara jaey, uski diyat key oonton mein sey chaalis oontniyaan aisi hon jinkey pet mein bachchey hon."
5052,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi ney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab fateh Makka key moqe par Makka Mukarrama tashrif laye to aap ney farmaya : aagah raho ! jo maqtool shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein ghalati sey kodey ya dandey, sauntey sey maara jaey, uski diyat key oonton mein sey chaalis oontniyaan aisi hon jinkey pet mein bachchey hon."
5053,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key saal Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to farmaya : khabrdar ! jo shakhs shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein kodey ya sauntey key sath ghalati sey qatl ho jaey, uski diyat mein sey chaalis oontniyaan aisi hon jinkey pet mein bachchey hon."
5054,"Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key saal Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil huye to farmaya : khabrdar ! jo shakhs shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein kodey ya sauntey key sath ghalati sey qatl ho jaey, uski diyat mein sey chaalis oontniyaan aisi hon jinkey pet mein bachchey hon."
5055,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key din Kaabey ki seedhi par khadey huye. aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki aur farmaya : sab tareef Allah Taala key liye hai jisney apna waada sachcha kar dikhaya aur apney bandey (Hazrat Muhammad Mustafa (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki madad farmaee, isi ke sath us akeley ney kuffar ki tamam jamaaton ko shikast sey dochaar kiya. suno ! jo shakhs shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein kodey ya sauntey key sath ghalti se maara jaey, uski diyat sakht hogi. (yani aisey) sau oont jin mein sey chaalis oontniyaan hamila hongi."
5056,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) fateh Makka key din Kaabey ki seedhi par khadey huye. aap ney Allah Taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki aur farmaya : sab tareef Allah Taala key liye hai jisney apna waada sachcha kar dikhaya aur apney bandey (Hazrat Muhammad Mustafa (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki madad farmaee, isi ke sath us akeley ney kuffar ki tamam jamaaton ko shikast sey dochaar kiya. suno ! jo shakhs shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein kodey ya sauntey key sath ghalti se maara jaey, uski diyat sakht hogi. (yani aisey) sau oont jin mein sey chaalis oontniyaan hamila hongi."
5057,"Hazrat Qasim bin Rabeea sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qatle-khata shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein, yani jo kodey ya sauntey key sath ho, is mein diyat sau oont hai jin mein sey chaalis oontniyaan hamila hon."
5058,"Hazrat Qasim bin Rabeea sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qatle-khata shib-hey-Amad ki surat mein, yani jo kodey ya sauntey key sath ho, is mein diyat sau oont hai jin mein sey chaalis oontniyaan hamila hon."
5059,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs khata (ghalati sey) maara jaey, uski diyat sau oont hai. tees binte makhaz (eik saala oontni), tees binte labun (do saala oontni), tees hiqqey (teen saala oontni) aur das ibne labun (eik saala muzakkir). unhon ( Abdullah bin Amr) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bastiyon (gaaun) main rehney waley logon par is diyat ki qeemat chaar sau deenar ya uskey barabar chaandi muqarrar farmatey they aur oonton walon par un ki qeemat waqt key lihaz sey aaid farmatey they. jab oont mahnge hotey to qeemat badha detey aur agar sastey ho jatey to qeemat kam lagatey, jo bhi hoti. aap key daure-mubarak mein ye qeemat chaar sau deenar sey aath sau deenar tak rahi ya uskey barabar chaandi thi. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla bhi farmaya ke jo shakhs gaayon sey diyat dena chahey to gaayon walon par diyat do sau gaey hogi aur jo shakhs bakriyon sey dena chahey to diyat do hazar bakri hogi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke diyat bhi virasat ki tarah maqtool key warison mein taqseem hogi. in ko unkey muqarrara hisson key mutabiq di jaeygi. agar koi maal bach jaey to wo maqtool key usba ko milega. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya tha ke aurat ki taraf sey diyat to uskey usba bharengey , jo bhi hon lekin wo uski virasat sey kuchh hasil nahin kerengey siwaey iske ke warison ko unkey muqarrara hisson ki adaegi key baad kuchh bach jaey (to wo bator usba in ko milega). aur agar koi aurat qatl kar di jaey to uski diyat warison mein taqseem hogi aur wohi qatil ko qatl kerengey (agar wo maaf na keren)."
5060,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs khata (ghalati sey) maara jaey, uski diyat sau oont hai. tees binte makhaz (eik saala oontni), tees binte labun (do saala oontni), tees hiqqey (teen saala oontni) aur das ibne labun (eik saala muzakkir). unhon ( Abdullah bin Amr) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bastiyon (gaaun) main rehney waley logon par is diyat ki qeemat chaar sau deenar ya uskey barabar chaandi muqarrar farmatey they aur oonton walon par un ki qeemat waqt key lihaz sey aaid farmatey they. jab oont mahnge hotey to qeemat badha detey aur agar sastey ho jatey to qeemat kam lagatey, jo bhi hoti. aap key daure-mubarak mein ye qeemat chaar sau deenar sey aath sau deenar tak rahi ya uskey barabar chaandi thi. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla bhi farmaya ke jo shakhs gaayon sey diyat dena chahey to gaayon walon par diyat do sau gaey hogi aur jo shakhs bakriyon sey dena chahey to diyat do hazar bakri hogi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke diyat bhi virasat ki tarah maqtool key warison mein taqseem hogi. in ko unkey muqarrara hisson key mutabiq di jaeygi. agar koi maal bach jaey to wo maqtool key usba ko milega. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya tha ke aurat ki taraf sey diyat to uskey usba bharengey , jo bhi hon lekin wo uski virasat sey kuchh hasil nahin kerengey siwaey iske ke warison ko unkey muqarrara hisson ki adaegi key baad kuchh bach jaey (to wo bator usba in ko milega). aur agar koi aurat qatl kar di jaey to uski diyat warison mein taqseem hogi aur wohi qatil ko qatl kerengey (agar wo maaf na keren)."
5061,Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qatle-khata ki diyat key barey mein faisla farmaya ke in mein bees binte-makhas (eik saala oontni) bees ibne makhaz (eik saala muzakkir) bees binte-labun (do saala oontni ) bees juzaa (chaar saala oontni) aur bees hiqqey (tees saala oontni) hongey.
5062,Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qatle-khata ki diyat key barey mein faisla farmaya ke in mein bees binte-makhas (eik saala oontni) bees ibne makhaz (eik saala muzakkir) bees binte-labun (do saala oontni ) bees juzaa (chaar saala oontni) aur bees hiqqey (tees saala oontni) hongey.
5063,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak main eik aadmi ney dusrey aadmi ko qatl kar diya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat baara hazar dirham muqarrar farmaee. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Allah Taala ka farman : (وَ ما نَقَمُوْٓا اِلَّآ اَنْ اَغْنٰہُمُ Allah ...),''aur nahin intiqam liya unhoney magar is baat ka ke Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool ney in ko apney Fazal sey ghani farmaya.'' diyat leney key barey mein hai. aur (mazkura ) alfaz abu-Daawood Harrani key hain."
5064,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak main eik aadmi ney dusrey aadmi ko qatl kar diya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat baara hazar dirham muqarrar farmaee. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Allah Taala ka farman : (وَ ما نَقَمُوْٓا اِلَّآ اَنْ اَغْنٰہُمُ Allah ...),''aur nahin intiqam liya unhoney magar is baat ka ke Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool ney in ko apney Fazal sey ghani farmaya.'' diyat leney key barey mein hai. aur (mazkura ) alfaz abu-Daawood Harrani key hain."
5065,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat baara hazar dirham muqarrar farmaee.
5066,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat baara hazar dirham muqarrar farmaee.
5067,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat ki diyat mard key barabar hai yahan tak ke tihai ko pahunch jaey.
5068,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat ki diyat mard key barabar hai yahan tak ke tihai ko pahunch jaey.
5069,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zimmi ki diyat musalman sey nisf (aadhi) hai. zimmi sey murad Yahud aur nasara hain.
5070,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zimmi ki diyat musalman sey nisf (aadhi) hai. zimmi sey murad Yahud aur nasara hain.
5071,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kafir ki diyat momin ki diyat sey nisf (aadhi) hai.
5072,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kafir ki diyat momin ki diyat sey nisf (aadhi) hai.
5073,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maktib key barey mein , jisey qatl kar diya jaey, faisla farmaya ke jis qadr wo makatibat (likhai) ada kar chuka hai, utni azad ki diyat di jaeygi."
5074,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maktib key barey mein , jisey qatl kar diya jaey, faisla farmaya ke jis qadr wo makatibat (likhai) ada kar chuka hai, utni azad ki diyat di jaeygi."
5075,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney makatib key barey mein faisla farmaya ke (agar wo qatl kar diya jaey to) jis qadr wo azad ho chuka hai, utni diyat azad ki di jaeygi."
5076,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney makatib key barey mein faisla farmaya ke (agar wo qatl kar diya jaey to) jis qadr wo azad ho chuka hai, utni diyat azad ki di jaeygi."
5077,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney makatib key barey mein faisla farmaya ke makatib ghulam jis qadr maale-makatibat (likhai) ada kar chuka hai, uski utni diyat azad key hisab sey di jaeygi aur baqi ghulam key lihaz sey."
5078,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney makatib key barey mein faisla farmaya ke makatib ghulam jis qadr maale-makatibat (likhai) ada kar chuka hai, uski utni diyat azad key hisab sey di jaeygi aur baqi ghulam key lihaz sey."
5079,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : makatib itna azad hai jis qadr wo makatibat (likhai) ada kar chuka hai aur wo jis qadr azad hai, utni is par had lagai jaeygi aur jis qadr wo azad hai, itna wo waris banega."
5080,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : makatib itna azad hai jis qadr wo makatibat (likhai) ada kar chuka hai aur wo jis qadr azad hai, utni is par had lagai jaeygi aur jis qadr wo azad hai, itna wo waris banega."
5081,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure mubarak main eik makatib ko qatl kar diya gaya to aap ney hukm diya ke jis qadr wo maale makatibat (likhaai) ada kar chuka hai, utney hissey ki diyat azad key hisab sey di jaey aur baqi ki ghulam key lihaz sey."
5082,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure mubarak main eik makatib ko qatl kar diya gaya to aap ney hukm diya ke jis qadr wo maale makatibat (likhaai) ada kar chuka hai, utney hissey ki diyat azad key hisab sey di jaey aur baqi ki ghulam key lihaz sey."
5083,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney dusri aurat ko patthar dey maara jis sey us ka hamal zaya ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us silsiley mein bachchey ki diyat pachas bakriyan muqarrar kein aur us din aap ney khazaf sey bhi mana farmaya. Abu Nuaim ney is riwayat ko mursal bayan kiya.
5084,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney dusri aurat ko patthar dey maara jis sey us ka hamal zaya ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us silsiley mein bachchey ki diyat pachas bakriyan muqarrar kein aur us din aap ney khazaf sey bhi mana farmaya. Abu Nuaim ney is riwayat ko mursal bayan kiya.
5085,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida ney bayan kiya ke eik aurat ney dusri aurat ko patthar dey maara jis sey us ka hamal zaya ho gaya. ye muqadma Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney pesh kiya gaya to aap ney us bachchey ki diyat paanch sau bakriyan muqarrar farmaai, isi ke sath us din aap ney khazaf sey rok diya. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain : ye weham hai. ho sakta hai ke unka irada eik sau bakriyan kehney ka ho (lekin ghalati sey paanch-sau bakriyan keh dein). aur khazaf, yani kankari phainkney ki mumaaniat to (Abdullah bin Barida, an Abdullah bin Mughaffal) sey marwi hai (aur wo agli hadees : 4819 hi hai.)"
5086,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida ney bayan kiya ke eik aurat ney dusri aurat ko patthar dey maara jis sey us ka hamal zaya ho gaya. ye muqadma Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney pesh kiya gaya to aap ney us bachchey ki diyat paanch sau bakriyan muqarrar farmaai, isi ke sath us din aap ney khazaf sey rok diya. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain : ye weham hai. ho sakta hai ke unka irada eik sau bakriyan kehney ka ho (lekin ghalati sey paanch-sau bakriyan keh dein). aur khazaf, yani kankari phainkney ki mumaaniat to (Abdullah bin Barida, an Abdullah bin Mughaffal) sey marwi hai (aur wo agli hadees : 4819 hi hai.)"
5087,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik aadmi ko khazaf kartey (kankari phainktey) dekha to farmaya : khazaf na kar kyonkey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khazaf (kankari phainktey) sey mana farmaya hai ya aap usey napasand farmatey they. (کَھْمَس) ko shak hai.
5088,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik aadmi ko khazaf kartey (kankari phainktey) dekha to farmaya : khazaf na kar kyonkey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khazaf (kankari phainktey) sey mana farmaya hai ya aap usey napasand farmatey they. (کَھْمَس) ko shak hai.
5089,Hazrat Taoos sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney pet key bachchey ki diyat key barey mein logon sey mashwara kiya to Hazrat Hamal bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurraa muqarrar farmaae hai. Hazrat Taoos ney kaha ke ghodaa bhi ghurra hai.
5090,Hazrat Taoos sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney pet key bachchey ki diyat key barey mein logon sey mashwara kiya to Hazrat Hamal bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurraa muqarrar farmaae hai. Hazrat Taoos ney kaha ke ghodaa bhi ghurra hai.
5091,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney banu Lihyaan ki eik aurat key pet key bachchey key barey mein jo (chot ki wajeh sey) saaqit ho kar mar gaya tha, faisla farmaya ke uski diyat ghurra hogi, yani ghulam ya londi. phir jis aurat key liye (jis key bachchey ki diyat ki baabat) ghurra ka faisla kiya tha, wo mar gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke uski virasat uskey beton aur khawind (shohar) ko milegi. aur us (qaatila) key zimmey wajibul-adaa diyat us (qaatila) key usba key zimmey hogi."
5092,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney banu Lihyaan ki eik aurat key pet key bachchey key barey mein jo (chot ki wajeh sey) saaqit ho kar mar gaya tha, faisla farmaya ke uski diyat ghurra hogi, yani ghulam ya londi. phir jis aurat key liye (jis key bachchey ki diyat ki baabat) ghurra ka faisla kiya tha, wo mar gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke uski virasat uskey beton aur khawind (shohar) ko milegi. aur us (qaatila) key zimmey wajibul-adaa diyat us (qaatila) key usba key zimmey hogi."
5093,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila Huzail ki do aurten aapas mein lad padin. eik ney dusri ko patthar dey maara. natije ke taur par usey bhi qatl kar diya aur uskey pet key bachchey ko bhi. wo (warisen) ye jhagda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra hai, yani eik ghulam ya londi, isi ke sath aap ney faisla farmaya ke (qaatila) aurat key zimmey wajibul-adaa diyat uskey usba bharengey. aur aap ney us (maqtoola) ki aulad aur deegar warison ko us ka waris banaya. Hazrat Hamal bin Malik bin Naabgha Hazli ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kaisey us (bachchey) ki diyat bharoon jisney na piya na khaya, na bola na chillaya? is jaisa (bachcha) to zaya aur laghw (fizul aur bekar) (bila diyat) hota hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to kaahinon mein sey eik kaahin mehsus hota hai. (aap ney ye baat farmaae) is liye ke us ney musajja'a kalam kiya tha."
5094,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila Huzail ki do aurten aapas mein lad padin. eik ney dusri ko patthar dey maara. natije ke taur par usey bhi qatl kar diya aur uskey pet key bachchey ko bhi. wo (warisen) ye jhagda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra hai, yani eik ghulam ya londi, isi ke sath aap ney faisla farmaya ke (qaatila) aurat key zimmey wajibul-adaa diyat uskey usba bharengey. aur aap ney us (maqtoola) ki aulad aur deegar warison ko us ka waris banaya. Hazrat Hamal bin Malik bin Naabgha Hazli ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kaisey us (bachchey) ki diyat bharoon jisney na piya na khaya, na bola na chillaya? is jaisa (bachcha) to zaya aur laghw (fizul aur bekar) (bila diyat) hota hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to kaahinon mein sey eik kaahin mehsus hota hai. (aap ney ye baat farmaae) is liye ke us ney musajja'a kalam kiya tha."
5095,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein qabila Huzail ki do aurton mein sey eik ney dusri ko patthar dey maara aur us ka hamal gira diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat ghrra muqarrar ki, yani eik ghulam ya londi."
5096,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein qabila Huzail ki do aurton mein sey eik ney dusri ko patthar dey maara aur us ka hamal gira diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat ghrra muqarrar ki, yani eik ghulam ya londi."
5097,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pet key us bachchey ki diyat jisey walida key pet mein qatl kar diya jaey, eik ghurra muqarrar farmaae hai, yani ghulam ya londi. jis shakhs key khilaf aap ney faisla farmaya tha, wo kehney laga : main us bachchey ki diyat kaisey bharoon jisney na piya na khaya, na cheekhaa na bola? aisa bachcha to zaya aur laghw hota hai (muaawzey ka haq-daar nahin hona chahiye). Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to kaahin (pujaari) lagta hai."
5098,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pet key us bachchey ki diyat jisey walida key pet mein qatl kar diya jaey, eik ghurra muqarrar farmaae hai, yani ghulam ya londi. jis shakhs key khilaf aap ney faisla farmaya tha, wo kehney laga : main us bachchey ki diyat kaisey bharoon jisney na piya na khaya, na cheekhaa na bola? aisa bachcha to zaya aur laghw hota hai (muaawzey ka haq-daar nahin hona chahiye). Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to kaahin (pujaari) lagta hai."
5099,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aurat ney apni saukan ko khemey ki lakdi dey maari aur usey qatl kar diya jabkey wo hamila thi. (lihaza hamal bhi zaya ho gaya). ye muqadma Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke qatil aurat key usba (maqtoola ki) diyat bharen, isi ke sath pet key bachchey key badley ghurra den. us aurat ka usba kehney laga : kya main aisey bachchey ki diyat dun jisney piya na khaya , cheekhaa na chillaya? aisa bachcha to kisi shumar aur qatar mein nahin hona chahiye. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to dehaatiyon jaisi tuk bandi karta hai."
5100,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aurat ney apni saukan ko khemey ki lakdi dey maari aur usey qatl kar diya jabkey wo hamila thi. (lihaza hamal bhi zaya ho gaya). ye muqadma Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke qatil aurat key usba (maqtoola ki) diyat bharen, isi ke sath pet key bachchey key badley ghurra den. us aurat ka usba kehney laga : kya main aisey bachchey ki diyat dun jisney piya na khaya , cheekhaa na chillaya? aisa bachcha to kisi shumar aur qatar mein nahin hona chahiye. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye to dehaatiyon jaisi tuk bandi karta hai."
5101,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aurat ney apni saukan ko khemey ka sutoon khinch maara jab ke wo hamila thi, wo mar gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtoola ki diyat qaatila key qaribi nasbi rishte-daaron par dal di. aur maqtoola key pet key bachchey ki diyat main eik ghurra lazim kiya. qaatila key rishte-daaron mein sey eik shakhs kehney laga : kya hum aisey bachchey ki diyat bharen jisney khaya na piya aur na choon ki? aisa bachcha to zaya aur laghw (fizul aur bekar) hota hai. aap ney farmaya : kya badduon jaisa musajja'a aur tukbandi wala kalam boltey ho? phir un par diyat laagu ki."
5102,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aurat ney apni saukan ko khemey ka sutoon khinch maara jab ke wo hamila thi, wo mar gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maqtoola ki diyat qaatila key qaribi nasbi rishte-daaron par dal di. aur maqtoola key pet key bachchey ki diyat main eik ghurra lazim kiya. qaatila key rishte-daaron mein sey eik shakhs kehney laga : kya hum aisey bachchey ki diyat bharen jisney khaya na piya aur na choon ki? aisa bachcha to zaya aur laghw (fizul aur bekar) hota hai. aap ney farmaya : kya badduon jaisa musajja'a aur tukbandi wala kalam boltey ho? phir un par diyat laagu ki."
5103,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke do sauknon mein sey eik ney dusri ko khemey ki lakdi dey maari aur usey qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat qaatila key nasbi rishte-daaron par dal di aur maqtoola key pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra qarar di. erabi (dehati) kehney laga : aap mujh par aisey bachchey ki diyat dal rahey hain jisney na khaya na piya, na cheekhaa na chillaya? aisa bachcha to zaya aur laghw hota hai. aap ney farmaya : zamanae-jahiliyat jaisi musajja'a o saji hui guftoogu ki hai. aap ney pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra muqarrar farmaae."
5104,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke do sauknon mein sey eik ney dusri ko khemey ki lakdi dey maari aur usey qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat qaatila key nasbi rishte-daaron par dal di aur maqtoola key pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra qarar di. erabi (dehati) kehney laga : aap mujh par aisey bachchey ki diyat dal rahey hain jisney na khaya na piya, na cheekhaa na chillaya? aisa bachcha to zaya aur laghw hota hai. aap ney farmaya : zamanae-jahiliyat jaisi musajja'a o saji hui guftoogu ki hai. aap ney pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra muqarrar farmaae."
5105,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : banu Lihyan ki eik aurat ney apni saukan ko khemey ki lakdi dey maari aur usey qatl kar diya. maqtoola ko hamal tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat qaatila key nasbi rishte-daaron par dal di aur us (maqtoola) key pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra muqarrar farmaae."
5106,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : banu Lihyan ki eik aurat ney apni saukan ko khemey ki lakdi dey maari aur usey qatl kar diya. maqtoola ko hamal tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uski diyat qaatila key nasbi rishte-daaron par dal di aur us (maqtoola) key pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra muqarrar farmaae."
5107,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Huzail key eik aadmi key nikah mein do aurten thin. eik ney dusri ko khemey ki lakdi dey maari aur uskey pet ka bacha gira diya. fareeqain jhagadtey huye Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. qatil ke fareeq kehney laga : hum is bachey ki kaisey diyat ada karen jisney piya na khaya, na cheekhaa na chaillaya? Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya dehaatiyon ki tarah tuk-bandi kar rahey ho? phir aap ney ghurra (ghulam ya londi bator diyat) qatil aurat key nasbi rishte-daaron key zimmey dal di."
5108,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Huzail key eik aadmi key nikah mein do aurten thin. eik ney dusri ko khemey ki lakdi dey maari aur uskey pet ka bacha gira diya. fareeqain jhagadtey huye Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. qatil ke fareeq kehney laga : hum is bachey ki kaisey diyat ada karen jisney piya na khaya, na cheekhaa na chaillaya? Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya dehaatiyon ki tarah tuk-bandi kar rahey ho? phir aap ney ghurra (ghulam ya londi bator diyat) qatil aurat key nasbi rishte-daaron key zimmey dal di."
5109,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Huzail key eik aadmi ki do biwiyan thin. eik ney dusri ko khemey ka sutoon dey maara aur us ka hamal gira diya. (jab aap ney bachchey ki diyat bayan farmaai to) aap sey kaha gaya : bataeyn to bhala jis bachchey ney na piya na khaya, na cheekhaa na chillaya (kya uski bhi diyat hogi?) aap ney farmaya : ye kya badduon jaisi tuk-bandi hai. phir aap ney uski diyat ghurra, yani eik ghulam ya londi muqarrar farmaaee aur usey aurat key nasbi rishte-daaron key zimmey dal diya. Aa'mash ney isey mursal bayan kiya hai."
5110,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Huzail key eik aadmi ki do biwiyan thin. eik ney dusri ko khemey ka sutoon dey maara aur us ka hamal gira diya. (jab aap ney bachchey ki diyat bayan farmaai to) aap sey kaha gaya : bataeyn to bhala jis bachchey ney na piya na khaya, na cheekhaa na chillaya (kya uski bhi diyat hogi?) aap ney farmaya : ye kya badduon jaisi tuk-bandi hai. phir aap ney uski diyat ghurra, yani eik ghulam ya londi muqarrar farmaaee aur usey aurat key nasbi rishte-daaron key zimmey dal diya. Aa'mash ney isey mursal bayan kiya hai."
5111,"Hazrat Ibrahim sey manqul hai ke eik aurat ney apni saukan ko patthar maara jabkey wo Hamila thi jis sey wo mar gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra (ghulam ya londi) muqarrar farmaae aur maqtoola ki diyat qaatila key nasbi rishte-daaron key zimmey dal di. unhoney kaha : hum aisey bachchey ki diyat bharen jisney piya na khaya, na choon-chaan ki? aisey bachchey ka to koi moawza nahin hona chahiye. aap ney farmaya : badduon ki tarah tuk-bandi kartey ho? asal hukm wohi hai jo main kehta hun."
5112,"Hazrat Ibrahim sey manqul hai ke eik aurat ney apni saukan ko patthar maara jabkey wo Hamila thi jis sey wo mar gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey pet key bachchey ki diyat ghurra (ghulam ya londi) muqarrar farmaae aur maqtoola ki diyat qaatila key nasbi rishte-daaron key zimmey dal di. unhoney kaha : hum aisey bachchey ki diyat bharen jisney piya na khaya, na choon-chaan ki? aisey bachchey ka to koi moawza nahin hona chahiye. aap ney farmaya : badduon ki tarah tuk-bandi kartey ho? asal hukm wohi hai jo main kehta hun."
5113,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : do saukanein thin. un mein jhagda ho gaya. eik ney dusri ko patthar dey maara aur uskey pet ka bachcha gira diya jo murda tha. uskey baal ug chukey they. aur aurat bhi mar gaee. aap ney qaatila key nasbi rishte-daaron par diyat dal di. maqtoola key chacha ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney bachcha bhi zaya kiya hai jis key baal ug chukey they. qaatila key walid ney kaha : ye jhoot boltaa hai. Allah ki qism ! ye bachcha na cheekhaa, chillaya, na us ney piya na khaya. aisa to zaya aur batil hota hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya jahilon aur kaahinon jaisi saja' (tuk-bandi) kar raha hai? is bachchey mein bhi ghurra aayega. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aurat ka naam Muleka aur dusri ka Ummey Ghateef tha."
5114,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : do saukanein thin. un mein jhagda ho gaya. eik ney dusri ko patthar dey maara aur uskey pet ka bachcha gira diya jo murda tha. uskey baal ug chukey they. aur aurat bhi mar gaee. aap ney qaatila key nasbi rishte-daaron par diyat dal di. maqtoola key chacha ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! is ney bachcha bhi zaya kiya hai jis key baal ug chukey they. qaatila key walid ney kaha : ye jhoot boltaa hai. Allah ki qism ! ye bachcha na cheekhaa, chillaya, na us ney piya na khaya. aisa to zaya aur batil hota hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya jahilon aur kaahinon jaisi saja' (tuk-bandi) kar raha hai? is bachchey mein bhi ghurra aayega. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aurat ka naam Muleka aur dusri ka Ummey Ghateef tha."
5115,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye tehreer likhwaai ke har qabiley ko apney logon par aaid-shuda deyaten deni hongi, isi ke sath kisi azad shuda ghulam key liye jayez nahin ke wo apney Mola ki ijazat key baghair kisi aur musalman ko Mola bana ley."
5116,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye tehreer likhwaai ke har qabiley ko apney logon par aaid-shuda deyaten deni hongi, isi ke sath kisi azad shuda ghulam key liye jayez nahin ke wo apney Mola ki ijazat key baghair kisi aur musalman ko Mola bana ley."
5117,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs aisey hi tabeeb (doctor) ban kar ilaj kerey. halanke (is sey qabl ) wo mustanad tabeeb nahin tha to (agar koi nuqsan ho jaey) wo zaamin (zimme-daar) hoga.
5118,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs aisey hi tabeeb (doctor) ban kar ilaj kerey. halanke (is sey qabl ) wo mustanad tabeeb nahin tha to (agar koi nuqsan ho jaey) wo zaamin (zimme-daar) hoga.
