5121,"Hazrat Abu Ramsa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas apney walid key sath hazir huwa. aap ney (merey walid sey) farmaya : ye terey sath kon hai? unhoney kaha : main gawahi deta hun, ye mera beta hai. aap ney farmaya : khabrdar ! terey jurm ka ye zimme-daar nahin aur to iskey jurm ka zimme-daar nahin."
5122,"Hazrat Abu Ramsa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas apney walid key sath hazir huwa. aap ney (merey walid sey) farmaya : ye terey sath kon hai? unhoney kaha : main gawahi deta hun, ye mera beta hai. aap ney farmaya : khabrdar ! terey jurm ka ye zimme-daar nahin aur to iskey jurm ka zimme-daar nahin."
5123,"Hazrat Solba bin Zehdam Yurbui (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ansaar key eik giroh mein khitab farma rahey they. ansaar kehney lagey : un banu Solba bin Yurbuaa ney jahiliyat mein falan shakhs ko qatl kar diya tha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aawaz buland kartey huye farmaya : aagah raho ! koi shakhs kisi dusrey key jurm ka zimme-daar nahin."
5124,"Hazrat Solba bin Zehdam Yurbui (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ansaar key eik giroh mein khitab farma rahey they. ansaar kehney lagey : un banu Solba bin Yurbuaa ney jahiliyat mein falan shakhs ko qatl kar diya tha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aawaz buland kartey huye farmaya : aagah raho ! koi shakhs kisi dusrey key jurm ka zimme-daar nahin."
5125,"Hazrat Solba bin Zehdam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : bano Solba key kuchh log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunchey jabkey aap khitab farma rahey they. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! in banu Solba bin Yurbuaa ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key falan sahabi ko qatl kiya tha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi shakhs key jurm ka koi doosra shakhs zimme-daar nahin hota."
5126,"Hazrat Solba bin Zehdam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : bano Solba key kuchh log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunchey jabkey aap khitab farma rahey they. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! in banu Solba bin Yurbuaa ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key falan sahabi ko qatl kiya tha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi shakhs key jurm ka koi doosra shakhs zimme-daar nahin hota."
5127,banu Solba bin Yurbuaa (qabiley) main sey eik shakhs sey riwayat hai ke banu Solba key kuchh log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! in banu Solba bin Yurbuaa ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key falan sahabi ko qatl kiya tha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs kisi dusrey key jurm ka zimme-daar nahin.
5128,banu Solba bin Yurbuaa (qabiley) main sey eik shakhs sey riwayat hai ke banu Solba key kuchh log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye to eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! in banu Solba bin Yurbuaa ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key falan sahabi ko qatl kiya tha. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs kisi dusrey key jurm ka zimme-daar nahin.
5129,banu Solba bin Yurbuaa key eik shakhs sey riwayat hai ke banu Solba key kuchh logon ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi ko qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye banu Solba hain. unhoney falan (sahabi) ko qatl kiya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi shakhs ka jurm kisi dusrey key naam nahin lag sakta. (raawi hadees) Shoba ney kaha : yani kisi ko kisi aur shakhs key jurm mein giraftar nahin kiya ja sakta. (wallahu-aalam).
5130,banu Solba bin Yurbuaa key eik shakhs sey riwayat hai ke banu Solba key kuchh logon ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi ko qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye banu Solba hain. unhoney falan (sahabi) ko qatl kiya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi shakhs ka jurm kisi dusrey key naam nahin lag sakta. (raawi hadees) Shoba ney kaha : yani kisi ko kisi aur shakhs key jurm mein giraftar nahin kiya ja sakta. (wallahu-aalam).
5131,banu Solba bin Yurbuaa key eik aadmi sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa jabkey aap khitab farma rahey they. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! in banu Solba bin Yurbuaa ney falan shakhs (sahabi Rasool) ko qatl kiya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin. yani kisi shakhs ka jurm kisi dusrey par nahin dala ja sakta.
5132,banu Solba bin Yurbuaa key eik aadmi sey riwayat hai ke main Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa jabkey aap khitab farma rahey they. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! in banu Solba bin Yurbuaa ney falan shakhs (sahabi Rasool) ko qatl kiya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin. yani kisi shakhs ka jurm kisi dusrey par nahin dala ja sakta.
5133,bani Yurbuaa key eik aadmi ney kaha : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunchey to aap logon sey khitab farma rahey they. (hamein dekh kar) kuchh log khadey ho gaey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye falan qabiley key log hain. inhoney falan sahabi ko qatl kiya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi eik shakhs ka jurm dusrey key zimmey nahin lagaya ja sakta.
5134,bani Yurbuaa key eik aadmi ney kaha : hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas pahunchey to aap logon sey khitab farma rahey they. (hamein dekh kar) kuchh log khadey ho gaey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye falan qabiley key log hain. inhoney falan sahabi ko qatl kiya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi eik shakhs ka jurm dusrey key zimmey nahin lagaya ja sakta.
5135,Hazrat Taariq Mahaaribi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye banu Solba hain jinhoney apney daure-jahiliyat mein falan ko qatl kiya tha. in sey hamein qisaas dilwa dijiye. aap ney apney haath mubarak uthaey yahan tak ke mainey aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhi. aap ney do dafa farmaya : kisi maa ka jurm uskey betey key galey nahin padta.
5136,Hazrat Taariq Mahaaribi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye banu Solba hain jinhoney apney daure-jahiliyat mein falan ko qatl kiya tha. in sey hamein qisaas dilwa dijiye. aap ney apney haath mubarak uthaey yahan tak ke mainey aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhi. aap ney do dafa farmaya : kisi maa ka jurm uskey betey key galey nahin padta.
5137,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke jo kaani (be Noor) aankh apni jagah qaaim ho, agar phod di jaey to aankh ki eik tihai diyat di jaeygi. aur be-jaan haath agar kaat diya jaey to haath ki tihai diyat dey di jaeygi. aur wo daant jo siyah ho chuka ho, ukhaad diya jaey to daant ki tihai diyat hogi."
5138,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke jo kaani (be Noor) aankh apni jagah qaaim ho, agar phod di jaey to aankh ki eik tihai diyat di jaeygi. aur be-jaan haath agar kaat diya jaey to haath ki tihai diyat dey di jaeygi. aur wo daant jo siyah ho chuka ho, ukhaad diya jaey to daant ki tihai diyat hogi."
5139,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : daanton mein paanch oont hain. yani har daant ki diyat paanch oont hai.
