5142,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab daant (diyat mein) barabar hain. yani har eik mein paanch paanch oont.
