5147,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke ungliyan sab barabar hain. (har eik ki diyat ) das das oont hai."
5148,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke ungliyan sab barabar hain. (har eik ki diyat ) das das oont hai."
5149,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai ke jab mainey wo dastawez dekhi jo Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) ki aulad key paas thi aur jis key barey mein unka daawey tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye tehreer khud likhwa kar in ko di, is mein ye bhi likha tha ke ungliyon ki diyat das das oont hai."
5150,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai ke jab mainey wo dastawez dekhi jo Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) ki aulad key paas thi aur jis key barey mein unka daawey tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye tehreer khud likhwa kar in ko di, is mein ye bhi likha tha ke ungliyon ki diyat das das oont hai."
5151,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aur ye barabar hain. yani angoothaa aur chhanguli.
5152,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aur ye barabar hain. yani angoothaa aur chhanguli.
5153,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke ye aur ye,  (yani) angoothaa aur chhanguli (diyat key lihaz sey) barabar hain."
5154,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke ye aur ye,  (yani) angoothaa aur chhanguli (diyat key lihaz sey) barabar hain."
5155,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : sab ungliyon ki diyat das das oont hai.
5156,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : sab ungliyon ki diyat das das oont hai.
5157,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Makka Mukarrama fatah kiya to apney khutbey mein irshad farmaya : ungliyon ki diyat das das oont hai."
5158,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Makka Mukarrama fatah kiya to apney khutbey mein irshad farmaya : ungliyon ki diyat das das oont hai."
5159,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney baap sey, wo (Shoaib) apney dada sey bayan kartey hain ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney khutbey mein farmaya jab ke aap ney Kaabe key sath apni pusht ki tek laga rakhi thi : tamam ungliyan (diyat key lihaz sey) barabar hain."
5160,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney baap sey, wo (Shoaib) apney dada sey bayan kartey hain ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney khutbey mein farmaya jab ke aap ney Kaabe key sath apni pusht ki tek laga rakhi thi : tamam ungliyan (diyat key lihaz sey) barabar hain."
5161,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Makka Mukarrama fatah kiya to apney khutbey mein irshad farmaya : haddi ko nangaa kar deney waley zakhmon mein diyat paanch paanch oont hai."
5162,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Makka Mukarrama fatah kiya to apney khutbey mein irshad farmaya : haddi ko nangaa kar deney waley zakhmon mein diyat paanch paanch oont hai."
5163,"Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Yamen walon ki taraf eik tehreer likhwa kar bheji jis mein faraaiz aur sunan aur diyat key masaayel they. aap ney wo tehreer Amr bin Hazam key haath bheji thi. wo ehale-Yamen ko padh kar sunai gaee. uski ibarat yun thi : ye tehreer Nabi Akram Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey Shurehbil bin Abd Kulaal, Nuaim bin Abd Kulaal aur Haris bin Abd Kulaal ki taraf hai, jo Zu-ruain, Muaafir aur Hamdaan key sardar hain. Amma-baad ! (us tehreer mein bahut si baaten thin ) us tehreer mein ye baat bhi thi ke jo shakhs kisi momin ko be gunah qatl kar dey aur gawah mojud hon to us ko qisas ke taur par qatl kar diya jaeyga siwaey iske ke maqtool key warison razi ho jaeyn. aur har insani jaan ki diyat sau oont hai. agar puri naak kaat di jaey to is mein mukammal diyat (sau oont) hogi. zaban puri kaat di jaey to is mein bhi puri diyat hogi. dono hont kaatey janey ki surat mein bhi puri diyat hogi. khasiyatein mukammal kaat diye jaeyn to puri diyat hogi. zikr pura kaat diya jaey to puri diyat hogi. kamar (reedh) ki haddi tod di jaey to puri diyat hogi. dono aankhen phod ya nikal di jaeyn to puri diyat hogi. eik paon ki nisf (aadhi) diyat hogi. dimagh tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein tihai diyat hogi. pet key andar tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein tihai diyat hogi. haddi ko tod deney waley zakham ki diyat pandarah oont hongey. haath paon ki ungliyon mein sey har ungli ki diyat das oont hogi. har daant ki diyat paanch oont hogi. haddi ko nangaa karney waley zakham ki diyat paanch oont hogi. aadmi aurat ko qatl karey to usey qatl kar diya jaeyga. agar koi shakhs soney ki surat mein diyat dena chahey to diyat eik hazar deenar hogi. Muhammad bin Bakkaar bin Bilal ney Hukm bin Musa ki mukhalifat ki hai."
5164,"Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Yamen walon ki taraf eik tehreer likhwa kar bheji jis mein faraaiz aur sunan aur diyat key masaayel they. aap ney wo tehreer Amr bin Hazam key haath bheji thi. wo ehale-Yamen ko padh kar sunai gaee. uski ibarat yun thi : ye tehreer Nabi Akram Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey Shurehbil bin Abd Kulaal, Nuaim bin Abd Kulaal aur Haris bin Abd Kulaal ki taraf hai, jo Zu-ruain, Muaafir aur Hamdaan key sardar hain. Amma-baad ! (us tehreer mein bahut si baaten thin ) us tehreer mein ye baat bhi thi ke jo shakhs kisi momin ko be gunah qatl kar dey aur gawah mojud hon to us ko qisas ke taur par qatl kar diya jaeyga siwaey iske ke maqtool key warison razi ho jaeyn. aur har insani jaan ki diyat sau oont hai. agar puri naak kaat di jaey to is mein mukammal diyat (sau oont) hogi. zaban puri kaat di jaey to is mein bhi puri diyat hogi. dono hont kaatey janey ki surat mein bhi puri diyat hogi. khasiyatein mukammal kaat diye jaeyn to puri diyat hogi. zikr pura kaat diya jaey to puri diyat hogi. kamar (reedh) ki haddi tod di jaey to puri diyat hogi. dono aankhen phod ya nikal di jaeyn to puri diyat hogi. eik paon ki nisf (aadhi) diyat hogi. dimagh tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein tihai diyat hogi. pet key andar tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein tihai diyat hogi. haddi ko tod deney waley zakham ki diyat pandarah oont hongey. haath paon ki ungliyon mein sey har ungli ki diyat das oont hogi. har daant ki diyat paanch oont hogi. haddi ko nangaa karney waley zakham ki diyat paanch oont hogi. aadmi aurat ko qatl karey to usey qatl kar diya jaeyga. agar koi shakhs soney ki surat mein diyat dena chahey to diyat eik hazar deenar hogi. Muhammad bin Bakkaar bin Bilal ney Hukm bin Musa ki mukhalifat ki hai."
5165,Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Yamen walon ki taraf eik tehreer likh kar bheji jis mein faraaiz aur sunan aur diyat key masaayel they. aap ney ye tehreer Hazrat Amr bin Hazam key haath bheji thi aur ye Yamen walon ko padh kar sunai gaee. ye us ka mazmoon hai. phir raawi ney sabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya magar us ney kaha : eik aankh mein nisf (aadhi) diyat (pachas oont) hai. eik haath mein nisf (aadhi) diyat hai aur eik paon mein nisf (aadhi) diyat hai. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke ye riwayat durust honey key ziyada qarib hai. (wallahu-aalam ! ) aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Arqam matrukul-hadees hai. aur yehi riwayat Yunus (bin Yazid) ney Imam Zohri (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey mursalan bayan ki hai jaisa ke darija-zail (ye likhi hui) riwayat hai.
5166,Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Yamen walon ki taraf eik tehreer likh kar bheji jis mein faraaiz aur sunan aur diyat key masaayel they. aap ney ye tehreer Hazrat Amr bin Hazam key haath bheji thi aur ye Yamen walon ko padh kar sunai gaee. ye us ka mazmoon hai. phir raawi ney sabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya magar us ney kaha : eik aankh mein nisf (aadhi) diyat (pachas oont) hai. eik haath mein nisf (aadhi) diyat hai aur eik paon mein nisf (aadhi) diyat hai. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke ye riwayat durust honey key ziyada qarib hai. (wallahu-aalam ! ) aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Arqam matrukul-hadees hai. aur yehi riwayat Yunus (bin Yazid) ney Imam Zohri (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey mursalan bayan ki hai jaisa ke darija-zail (ye likhi hui) riwayat hai.
5167,"Hazrat ibne-Shahab (Zohri) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wo tehreer padhi hai jo aap ney Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) ko Najran ka Haakim banatey waqt likh kar di thi. ye tehreer Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Hazam key paas thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney likha tha ke ye Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool ki taraf sey (ehkam ka) bayan hai : aey eman walo ! ehad purey karo. phir aap ney chand aayaat likhin. yahan tak ke yahan tak pahunchey : (ان اللہ سریع الحساب),''be shak Allah bahut jald hisab leney wala hai.''phir aap ney tehreer farmaya tha ke ye zakhmon waghera (ki diyat) key barey main eik tehreer hai. jaan (khatam kar deney ki soorat) main diyat sau oont hogi. baqi pichhli riwayat ke hisab se hai."
5168,"Hazrat ibne-Shahab (Zohri) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wo tehreer padhi hai jo aap ney Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) ko Najran ka Haakim banatey waqt likh kar di thi. ye tehreer Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Hazam key paas thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney likha tha ke ye Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool ki taraf sey (ehkam ka) bayan hai : aey eman walo ! ehad purey karo. phir aap ney chand aayaat likhin. yahan tak ke yahan tak pahunchey : (ان اللہ سریع الحساب),''be shak Allah bahut jald hisab leney wala hai.''phir aap ney tehreer farmaya tha ke ye zakhmon waghera (ki diyat) key barey main eik tehreer hai. jaan (khatam kar deney ki soorat) main diyat sau oont hogi. baqi pichhli riwayat ke hisab se hai."
5169,"Hazrat Zohri (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey paas Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Hazam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki tehreer ley kar aaye jo chamdey key tukdey par likhi hui thi ke ye Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool ki taraf sey (ehkam ka) bayan hai : aey eman walo ! ehad purey karo. phir uskey baad kaee aayaten padhin phir kaha : (phir likha tha) kisi jaan ko khatam kar deney ki surat mein diyat sau oont hogi. eik haath mein pachas oont hain. eik aankh mein (aankh ki diyat) pachas oont hain aur eik paon ki diyat bhi pachas oont hain. dimagh tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein tihai diyat hai. aur pet key andar tak pahunch janey waley zakham ki diyat bhi eik tihai hai. haddi ko tod deney waley zakham mein pandarah oont diyat hai. ungliyon ki diyat das das oont hai. daanton ki diyat paanch paanch oont hai. aur haddi ko nangaa karney waley zakham mein paanch oont diyat hai."
5170,"Hazrat Zohri (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey paas Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Hazam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki tehreer ley kar aaye jo chamdey key tukdey par likhi hui thi ke ye Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool ki taraf sey (ehkam ka) bayan hai : aey eman walo ! ehad purey karo. phir uskey baad kaee aayaten padhin phir kaha : (phir likha tha) kisi jaan ko khatam kar deney ki surat mein diyat sau oont hogi. eik haath mein pachas oont hain. eik aankh mein (aankh ki diyat) pachas oont hain aur eik paon ki diyat bhi pachas oont hain. dimagh tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein tihai diyat hai. aur pet key andar tak pahunch janey waley zakham ki diyat bhi eik tihai hai. haddi ko tod deney waley zakham mein pandarah oont diyat hai. ungliyon ki diyat das das oont hai. daanton ki diyat paanch paanch oont hai. aur haddi ko nangaa karney waley zakham mein paanch oont diyat hai."
5171,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Muhammad bin Amr bin Hazam sey riwayat hai ke wo tehreer jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat key masaayel key barey mein Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) ko likh kar di thi. (yun hai ke) jaan (khatam kar deney ki soorat) main sau oont diyat hai. aur naak mein, jab wo jad sey kaat di jaey, bhi sau oont diyat hai. aur dimagh tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein kul diyat ka eik tihai hai. aur pet key andar pahunch janey waley zakham mein bhi tihai diyat hi hai. eik haath mein pachas oont diyat hai. aur eik aankh mein bhi pachas oont hain aur eik paon mein bhi pachas oont hain. aur (haath paon ki) har ungli mein das oont diyat hai. har daant mein paanch oont hain aur haddi ko nangaa kar deney waley zakham mein bhi paanch oont diyat hai."
5172,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Muhammad bin Amr bin Hazam sey riwayat hai ke wo tehreer jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney diyat key masaayel key barey mein Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) ko likh kar di thi. (yun hai ke) jaan (khatam kar deney ki soorat) main sau oont diyat hai. aur naak mein, jab wo jad sey kaat di jaey, bhi sau oont diyat hai. aur dimagh tak pahunch janey waley zakham mein kul diyat ka eik tihai hai. aur pet key andar pahunch janey waley zakham mein bhi tihai diyat hi hai. eik haath mein pachas oont diyat hai. aur eik aankh mein bhi pachas oont hain aur eik paon mein bhi pachas oont hain. aur (haath paon ki) har ungli mein das oont diyat hai. har daant mein paanch oont hain aur haddi ko nangaa kar deney waley zakham mein bhi paanch oont diyat hai."
5173,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik erabi (dehati) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key darwazey key paas aaya aur us ney apni aankh darwazey key surakh par laga di. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko dekh liya aur aap eik tez dhaar wali chiz ya eik (nauk-daar) lakdi ley kar uski taraf chaley taake uski aankh phod den. jab us ney aap ko (aatey) dekha to aankh peechhey hata li. (peechhey hat gaya) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey (ghussey key sath ) farmaya : agar to isi tarah khada rehta to main teri aankh phod deta.
5174,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik erabi (dehati) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key darwazey key paas aaya aur us ney apni aankh darwazey key surakh par laga di. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko dekh liya aur aap eik tez dhaar wali chiz ya eik (nauk-daar) lakdi ley kar uski taraf chaley taake uski aankh phod den. jab us ney aap ko (aatey) dekha to aankh peechhey hata li. (peechhey hat gaya) Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey (ghussey key sath ) farmaya : agar to isi tarah khada rehta to main teri aankh phod deta.
5175,Hazrat Sahal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di ke eik aadmi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key darwazey key surakh sey jhankney laga. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik naukdaar lakdi thi jis sey aap apney sar ko khujli farma rahey they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko dekha to farmaya : agar mujhey ilm hota ke to mujhey dekh raha hai to main ye lakdi teri aankh mein maar deta. ijazat leney ka hukm to isi liye diya gaya hai ke nazar na pad sakey.
5176,Hazrat Sahal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di ke eik aadmi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key darwazey key surakh sey jhankney laga. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik naukdaar lakdi thi jis sey aap apney sar ko khujli farma rahey they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ko dekha to farmaya : agar mujhey ilm hota ke to mujhey dekh raha hai to main ye lakdi teri aankh mein maar deta. ijazat leney ka hukm to isi liye diya gaya hai ke nazar na pad sakey.
5177,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi key ghar mein baghair ijazat liye jhaankney lagey aur wo uski aankh phod den to us ko diyat milegi na qisaas.
5178,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi key ghar mein baghair ijazat liye jhaankney lagey aur wo uski aankh phod den to us ko diyat milegi na qisaas.
5179,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar koi shakhs tujhey baghair ijazat jhaankney lagey aur to kankari waghera maar kar uski aankh phod dey to tujh par koi tawaan (jurmaana) aur gunah aaid nahin hoga.
5180,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar koi shakhs tujhey baghair ijazat jhaankney lagey aur to kankari waghera maar kar uski aankh phod dey to tujh par koi tawaan (jurmaana) aur gunah aaid nahin hoga.
5181,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo namaz padh rahey they. itney mein Hazrat Marwan ka eik beta unkey aagey sey guzarney laga. unhoney us ko peechhey dhakela lekin wo peechhey na hata to unhoney usey maara. wo rotaa huwa chala gaya yahan tak ke Hazrat Marwan key paas pahunch gaya aur ja kar unhein bataya. Hazrat Marwan ney Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap ney apney bhateejey (merey betey) ko kyon maara hai? unhoney kaha : mainey us ko nahin maara. mainey to shetan ko maara hai. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs namaz padh raha ho aur koi doosra shakhs uskey aagey sey guzarnaa chahey to wo apni taqat ki had tak usey rokney ki koshish kerey. agar wo (rukney sey) inkar kar dey (aur rokney key bawajud phir bhi guzarney par Misr rahey) to us sey ladey kyonkey wo shetan hai.
5182,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo namaz padh rahey they. itney mein Hazrat Marwan ka eik beta unkey aagey sey guzarney laga. unhoney us ko peechhey dhakela lekin wo peechhey na hata to unhoney usey maara. wo rotaa huwa chala gaya yahan tak ke Hazrat Marwan key paas pahunch gaya aur ja kar unhein bataya. Hazrat Marwan ney Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap ney apney bhateejey (merey betey) ko kyon maara hai? unhoney kaha : mainey us ko nahin maara. mainey to shetan ko maara hai. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs namaz padh raha ho aur koi doosra shakhs uskey aagey sey guzarnaa chahey to wo apni taqat ki had tak usey rokney ki koshish kerey. agar wo (rukney sey) inkar kar dey (aur rokney key bawajud phir bhi guzarney par Misr rahey) to us sey ladey kyonkey wo shetan hai.
5183,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi (Raziallahu anhu) ney hukm diya ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey un do aayaat key barey mein poochhun : (وَ مَنْ یَّقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا مُّتَعَمِّدًا),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey, uski saza jahannam hai.'' ''Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : is aayat ko kisi dusri aayat ney mansookh nahin kiya. dusri aayat ye thi : (وَالَّذِیْنَ لَا یَدْعُوْنَ مَعَ اللّٰہِ),''aur wo log jo Allah Taala key sath kisi aur ko mabood nahin banatey aur kisi qabile-ehtiraam jaan ko nahaq qatl nahin kartey.'' unhoney farmaya : ye mushrekin key barey mein utri hai."
5184,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi (Raziallahu anhu) ney hukm diya ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey un do aayaat key barey mein poochhun : (وَ مَنْ یَّقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا مُّتَعَمِّدًا),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey, uski saza jahannam hai.'' ''Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : is aayat ko kisi dusri aayat ney mansookh nahin kiya. dusri aayat ye thi : (وَالَّذِیْنَ لَا یَدْعُوْنَ مَعَ اللّٰہِ),''aur wo log jo Allah Taala key sath kisi aur ko mabood nahin banatey aur kisi qabile-ehtiraam jaan ko nahaq qatl nahin kartey.'' unhoney farmaya : ye mushrekin key barey mein utri hai."
5185,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Kufaa walon ka is aayat key barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya : (وَ مَنْ یَّقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا مُّتَعَمِّدًا),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kerey.'' mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf kooch kiya aur un sey ye masla puchha to unhoney farmaya : ye aayat aakhiri nazil honey wali aayaat mein shamil hai. is ko kisi aur aayat ney mansookh nahin kiya."
5186,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Kufaa walon ka is aayat key barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya : (وَ مَنْ یَّقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا مُّتَعَمِّدًا),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kerey.'' mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf kooch kiya aur un sey ye masla puchha to unhoney farmaya : ye aayat aakhiri nazil honey wali aayaat mein shamil hai. is ko kisi aur aayat ney mansookh nahin kiya."
5187,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey, kya uski tauba qubul ho sakti hai? unhoney farmaya : nahin. mainey Sura furqan wali aayat padhi : (وَالَّذِیْنَ لَا یَدْعُوْنَ . . . . . ),''woh log jo Allah Taala key sath kisi ko mabood nahin banatey aur na kisi qabile-ehtiraam jaan ko nahaq qatl kartey hain magar haq key sath.'' unhoney farmaya : ye aayat Makki daur mein utri. is ko Madina Munawra mein utarney wali eik aayat ney mansookh kar diya : (وَ مَنْ یَّقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا مُّتَعَمِّدًا . . . . . ), ''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan-bujh kar qatl kerey. uski saza jahannam hai.''"
5188,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey, kya uski tauba qubul ho sakti hai? unhoney farmaya : nahin. mainey Sura furqan wali aayat padhi : (وَالَّذِیْنَ لَا یَدْعُوْنَ . . . . . ),''woh log jo Allah Taala key sath kisi ko mabood nahin banatey aur na kisi qabile-ehtiraam jaan ko nahaq qatl kartey hain magar haq key sath.'' unhoney farmaya : ye aayat Makki daur mein utri. is ko Madina Munawra mein utarney wali eik aayat ney mansookh kar diya : (وَ مَنْ یَّقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا مُّتَعَمِّدًا . . . . . ), ''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan-bujh kar qatl kerey. uski saza jahannam hai.''"
5189,"Hazrat Salim bin Abul-Ja'd (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jo kisi momin shakhs ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey. phir tauba kerey. eman ley aaye aur nek amal shuru kar dey. phir raahe-raast par aa jaey. (kya uski tauba qubul hai?) Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : uskey liye tauba ki gunjaaish kaisey ho sakti hai? mainey tumharey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : maqtool qatil ko pakad kar layega jab ke maqtool ki ragon sey khoon beh raha hoga aur wo keh raha hoga : ya-Allah ! is sey poochh, is ney mujhey kis bina par qatl kiya? phir farmaya : Allah ki qism ! ye (pichhli hadees mein mazkur) aayat Allah Taala ney utaari hai aur isey mansookh nahin farmaya."
5190,"Hazrat Salim bin Abul-Ja'd (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jo kisi momin shakhs ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey. phir tauba kerey. eman ley aaye aur nek amal shuru kar dey. phir raahe-raast par aa jaey. (kya uski tauba qubul hai?) Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : uskey liye tauba ki gunjaaish kaisey ho sakti hai? mainey tumharey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : maqtool qatil ko pakad kar layega jab ke maqtool ki ragon sey khoon beh raha hoga aur wo keh raha hoga : ya-Allah ! is sey poochh, is ney mujhey kis bina par qatl kiya? phir farmaya : Allah ki qism ! ye (pichhli hadees mein mazkur) aayat Allah Taala ney utaari hai aur isey mansookh nahin farmaya."
5191,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kabeera gunah ye hain : Allah Taala key sath shareek banana, waliden ki nafarmani karna, kisi (be-gunah) ko qatl karna aur jhooti baat karna."
5192,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kabeera gunah ye hain : Allah Taala key sath shareek banana, waliden ki nafarmani karna, kisi (be-gunah) ko qatl karna aur jhooti baat karna."
5193,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey badey gunah ye hain : Allah Taala key sath shareek thehrana, maa baap ki nafarmani karna, kisi be-gunah jaan ko qatl karna aur jhooti qism khana."
5194,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey badey gunah ye hain : Allah Taala key sath shareek thehrana, maa baap ki nafarmani karna, kisi be-gunah jaan ko qatl karna aur jhooti qism khana."
5195,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi banda zina karta hai to wo momin nahin rehta. jab koi sharab peeta hai to sharab peetey waqt momin nahin rehta. jab koi chori karta hai to momin nahin rehta aur qatl karta hai to bhi momin nahin rehta.
5196,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi banda zina karta hai to wo momin nahin rehta. jab koi sharab peeta hai to sharab peetey waqt momin nahin rehta. jab koi chori karta hai to momin nahin rehta aur qatl karta hai to bhi momin nahin rehta.
5197,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs zina karta hai to wo momin nahin hota. jab koi shakhs chori karta hai to wo sahbe-emaan nahin hota. jab koi shakhs sharab peeta hai to wo eman sey la-taaluq ho jata hai. aur jab koi shakhs taqat aur quwat key zor par zabardasti daaka daalta hai ke log be-chaarey dekhtey reh jatey hain to wo bhi eman sey khaali hota hai.
5198,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs zina karta hai to wo momin nahin hota. jab koi shakhs chori karta hai to wo sahbe-emaan nahin hota. jab koi shakhs sharab peeta hai to wo eman sey la-taaluq ho jata hai. aur jab koi shakhs taqat aur quwat key zor par zabardasti daaka daalta hai ke log be-chaarey dekhtey reh jatey hain to wo bhi eman sey khaali hota hai.
5199,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zaani jab zina karta hai to momin nahin hota. chor jab chori karta hai to momin nahin hota. aur shraabi jab sharab peeta hai to momin nahin hota. albatta tauba phir bhi ho sakti hai.
5200,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zaani jab zina karta hai to momin nahin hota. chor jab chori karta hai to momin nahin hota. aur shraabi jab sharab peeta hai to momin nahin hota. albatta tauba phir bhi ho sakti hai.
5201,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab koi shakhs zina karta hai to wo momin nahin hota. aur (jab koi shakhs) chori karta hai to wo momin nahin hota aur (jab) sharab peeta hai to momin nahin hota. unhoney eik chauthi chiz ka bhi zikr farmaya lekin main bhool gaya. jo aadmi ye kaam karta hai wo Islam ka toq apni gardan sey utaar deta hai lekin agar wo tauba karey to Allah Taala uski tauba qubul farma leta hai.
5202,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab koi shakhs zina karta hai to wo momin nahin hota. aur (jab koi shakhs) chori karta hai to wo momin nahin hota aur (jab) sharab peeta hai to momin nahin hota. unhoney eik chauthi chiz ka bhi zikr farmaya lekin main bhool gaya. jo aadmi ye kaam karta hai wo Islam ka toq apni gardan sey utaar deta hai lekin agar wo tauba karey to Allah Taala uski tauba qubul farma leta hai.
5203,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala chor par lanat karey wo andaa churaa leta hai to us ka haath kaat diya jata hai. rassi churaa leta hai to us ka haath kaat diya jata hai.
5204,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala chor par lanat karey wo andaa churaa leta hai to us ka haath kaat diya jata hai. rassi churaa leta hai to us ka haath kaat diya jata hai.
5205,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke banu Kalaa key kuchh logon ney unkey paas muqadma pesh kiya ke kapda bananey waley kuchh logon ney hamara saman churaa liya hai. unhoney in ko chand din qaid mein rakha, phir chhod diya. muqadma pesh karney waley aaye aur kaha : aap ney in ko baghair kisi maar pit aur tehqiq aur chhaanbeen key chhod diya hai? Hazrat Noman ney farmaya : tum kya chahtey ho? agar tum chaho to main in ko maar-pit karta hun. agar tumhara saman un sey baraamat ho gaya to behtar warna main tumhari peethon par bhi utni hi maar-peet karunga. unhoney kaha : ye aap ka faisla hai? unhoney farmaya : ye Allah Taala ka faisla hai uskey Rasool mukarram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla hai."
5206,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke banu Kalaa key kuchh logon ney unkey paas muqadma pesh kiya ke kapda bananey waley kuchh logon ney hamara saman churaa liya hai. unhoney in ko chand din qaid mein rakha, phir chhod diya. muqadma pesh karney waley aaye aur kaha : aap ney in ko baghair kisi maar pit aur tehqiq aur chhaanbeen key chhod diya hai? Hazrat Noman ney farmaya : tum kya chahtey ho? agar tum chaho to main in ko maar-pit karta hun. agar tumhara saman un sey baraamat ho gaya to behtar warna main tumhari peethon par bhi utni hi maar-peet karunga. unhoney kaha : ye aap ka faisla hai? unhoney farmaya : ye Allah Taala ka faisla hai uskey Rasool mukarram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla hai."
5207,Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim apney baap sey wo (Bahaz) unkey dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qusheri (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh logon ko eik ilzam mein qaid kar diya tha.
5208,Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim apney baap sey wo (Bahaz) unkey dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qusheri (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh logon ko eik ilzam mein qaid kar diya tha.
5209,"Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim key dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qusheri (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko kisi ilzam mein qaid kar diya tha, phir (ilzam sabit na honey par) usey chhod diya."
5210,"Hazrat Bahaz bin Hakim key dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qusheri (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko kisi ilzam mein qaid kar diya tha, phir (ilzam sabit na honey par) usey chhod diya."
5211,Hazrat Abu Umaiya Makhzoomi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya jisney khud-ba-khud chori ka aetraaf kiya tha lekin uskey paas (chori ka) saman nahin mila tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : main nahin samajhta ke tu ney chori ki hogi. us ney kaha : kyon nahin (balke ki hai). aap ney farmaya : isey ley jao aur iska haath kaat kar phir merey paas ley aao. wo us ka haath kaat kar usey wapis laye to aap ney usey farmaya : keh main Allah Taala sey bakhshish talab karta hun aur tauba karta hun. us ney yehi alfaz dohra diye. aap ney farmaya : aey Allah ! iski tauba qubul farma.
5212,Hazrat Abu Umaiya Makhzoomi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya jisney khud-ba-khud chori ka aetraaf kiya tha lekin uskey paas (chori ka) saman nahin mila tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : main nahin samajhta ke tu ney chori ki hogi. us ney kaha : kyon nahin (balke ki hai). aap ney farmaya : isey ley jao aur iska haath kaat kar phir merey paas ley aao. wo us ka haath kaat kar usey wapis laye to aap ney usey farmaya : keh main Allah Taala sey bakhshish talab karta hun aur tauba karta hun. us ney yehi alfaz dohra diye. aap ney farmaya : aey Allah ! iski tauba qubul farma.
5213,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney un ki chadar churaa li. wo usey (chor ko) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye to aap ney us ka haath kaat deney ka hukm diya. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey is ko maaf kar diya. aap ney farmaya : Abu-Wahab ! (maaf hi karna tha tu) hamarey paas laney sey pehley kyon maaf na kar diya? phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uska haath kaat diya.
5214,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney un ki chadar churaa li. wo usey (chor ko) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye to aap ney us ka haath kaat deney ka hukm diya. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey is ko maaf kar diya. aap ney farmaya : Abu-Wahab ! (maaf hi karna tha tu) hamarey paas laney sey pehley kyon maaf na kar diya? phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uska haath kaat diya.
5215,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney (meri) chadar churaa li. wo usey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey. aap ney us ka haath kaat deney ka hukm diya. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey isey maaf kar diya. aap ney farmaya : Abu-Wahab ! tu ney ye kaam merey paas pesh karney sey pehley kyon na kiya? phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ka haath kaat diya.
5216,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney (meri) chadar churaa li. wo usey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley gaey. aap ney us ka haath kaat deney ka hukm diya. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey isey maaf kar diya. aap ney farmaya : Abu-Wahab ! tu ney ye kaam merey paas pesh karney sey pehley kyon na kiya? phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ka haath kaat diya.
5217,Hazrat Ata bin Abu Ribaah sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kapda churaa liya. usey pakad kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. aap ney us ka haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya. (kapdey waley) aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye kapda is ko maaf hai. aap ney farmaya : is waqt sey pehley kyon na (maaf) kiya.
5218,Hazrat Ata bin Abu Ribaah sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kapda churaa liya. usey pakad kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. aap ney us ka haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya. (kapdey waley) aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye kapda is ko maaf hai. aap ney farmaya : is waqt sey pehley kyon na (maaf) kiya.
5219,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Baitullah ka tawaf kiya phir namaz padhi phir apni chadar tahiya kar key apney sar key nichey rakh li aur sau gaey. eik chor aaya aur us ney wo chadar unkey sar key nichey sey khiska li. unhoney usey pakad liya aur Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye aur kaha : is ney meri chadar churaai hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey puchha : tu ney iski chadar churaai hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney (do aadmiyon ko) hukm diya : isey ley jao aur is ka haath kaat do. Safwan ney kaha : mera ye maqsad nahin tha ke aap meri chadar ki bina par is ka haath kaat den. aap ney farmaya : is sey pehley kyon (maaf) na kiya. Ash-as bin Sawar ney iski mukhalifat ki hai.
5220,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Baitullah ka tawaf kiya phir namaz padhi phir apni chadar tahiya kar key apney sar key nichey rakh li aur sau gaey. eik chor aaya aur us ney wo chadar unkey sar key nichey sey khiska li. unhoney usey pakad liya aur Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye aur kaha : is ney meri chadar churaai hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey puchha : tu ney iski chadar churaai hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney (do aadmiyon ko) hukm diya : isey ley jao aur is ka haath kaat do. Safwan ney kaha : mera ye maqsad nahin tha ke aap meri chadar ki bina par is ka haath kaat den. aap ney farmaya : is sey pehley kyon (maaf) na kiya. Ash-as bin Sawar ney iski mukhalifat ki hai.
5221,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Safwan masjid mein soey huye they jabkey un ki chadar unkey (sar key) nichey thi. wo churaa li gaee. in ko jaag aai to chor ja chuka tha. unhoney bhag kar usey pakad liya aur Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye. aap ney chor ka haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya. Safwan ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri chadar itni qeemti to nahin ke iski bina par kisi aadmi ka haath kaat diya jaey? aap ney farmaya : ye baat is ko merey paas laney sey pehley kyon na sochi. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) ney farmaya : (is riwayat ka raawi ) Ash-as Zaeef hai (maqsad ye hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas ka zikr is riwayat mein sahih nahin).
5222,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Safwan masjid mein soey huye they jabkey un ki chadar unkey (sar key) nichey thi. wo churaa li gaee. in ko jaag aai to chor ja chuka tha. unhoney bhag kar usey pakad liya aur Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye. aap ney chor ka haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya. Safwan ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri chadar itni qeemti to nahin ke iski bina par kisi aadmi ka haath kaat diya jaey? aap ney farmaya : ye baat is ko merey paas laney sey pehley kyon na sochi. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) ney farmaya : (is riwayat ka raawi ) Ash-as Zaeef hai (maqsad ye hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas ka zikr is riwayat mein sahih nahin).
5223,"Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main masjid mein apni munaqqash (dhaari daar) chadar par soyaa huwa tha jiski qeemat tees dirham thi. eik aadmi aaya aur usey khiska ley gaya. wo aadmi pakda gaya aur Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. aap ney us ka haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya. main aap key paas aaya aur arz kiya : aap sirf tees dirham key badley is ka haath kaat rahey hain? main ye chadar is ko bech deta hun. qeemat is sey baad mein ley lunga. aap ney farmaya : ye sab kuchh merey paas muqadma laney sey pehley kyon na kiya?"
5224,"Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main masjid mein apni munaqqash (dhaari daar) chadar par soyaa huwa tha jiski qeemat tees dirham thi. eik aadmi aaya aur usey khiska ley gaya. wo aadmi pakda gaya aur Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. aap ney us ka haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya. main aap key paas aaya aur arz kiya : aap sirf tees dirham key badley is ka haath kaat rahey hain? main ye chadar is ko bech deta hun. qeemat is sey baad mein ley lunga. aap ney farmaya : ye sab kuchh merey paas muqadma laney sey pehley kyon na kiya?"
5225,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke merey sar key nichey sey eik dhaari daar chadar churaa li gaee jabkey wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki masjid mein soey huye they. wo chor ko pakad kar Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye. aap ney us ka haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya. Safwan ney kaha : aap (itni chiz mein) iska haath kaat dengey? (main isey maaf karta hun). aap ney farmaya : tu ney isey merey paas laney sey pehley kyon na chhod diya?
5226,Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke merey sar key nichey sey eik dhaari daar chadar churaa li gaee jabkey wo Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki masjid mein soey huye they. wo chor ko pakad kar Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ley aaye. aap ney us ka haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya. Safwan ney kaha : aap (itni chiz mein) iska haath kaat dengey? (main isey maaf karta hun). aap ney farmaya : tu ney isey merey paas laney sey pehley kyon na chhod diya?
